#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:2
msgid "创建产品"
msgstr "Create a Product"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:4
msgid "**此页面的用途**"
msgstr "**What this page covers**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:6
msgid ""
"本页说明如何通过 **自动编程向导** 完整创建一个新的 PCBA 产品。向导共四步：基本信息、上板与拍摄、配置自动编程、添加CAD（最后一步见 "
":doc:`auto_programming`）。"
msgstr ""
"This page explains how to create a new PCBA product end-to-end with the "
"**Auto-Programming Wizard**. The wizard has four steps: Basic Info, Conveyor"
" & Capture, Configure Auto-Program, and Add CAD (the last step is covered in"
" :doc:`auto_programming`)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:8
msgid "**如何进入**"
msgstr "**How to open it**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:10
msgid "在主页点击 **训练PCBA** 按钮，进入 **自动编程向导**。向导将自动停在第一步 **基本信息**。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Train PCBA** on the home page to open the **Auto-Programming "
"wizard**. It opens on step 1 — **Basic Info**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:-1
msgid "主页「训练PCBA」入口卡片"
msgstr "Home page *Train PCBA* entry card"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:17
msgid "自动编程向导需要一次完成。如果在中途退出，则无法重新回到之前的步骤。如果不小心中途退出，可以删除当前未完成的产品，重新创建一个新的产品。"
msgstr ""
"The Auto-Programming wizard must be completed in one pass. There is no way "
"to resume a partially-finished wizard. If you exit by accident, delete the "
"half-finished product and start a new one."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:19
msgid "**操作流程**"
msgstr "**Workflow**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:21
msgid "**第一步：填写基本信息**"
msgstr "**Step 1: Fill in Basic Info**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:23
msgid "在 **基本信息** 步骤中填写以下内容，完成后点击 **下一步**："
msgstr ""
"On the **Basic Info** step, fill in the following, then click **Next**:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:25
msgid "**产品名称** — 输入唯一的产品名称。若名称已存在，系统将提示\"名称重复\"错误，需重新输入。"
msgstr ""
"**Product Name** — enter a unique product name. If the name already exists, "
"the system returns a \"Name duplicated\" error and you must re-enter it."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:27
msgid "**标签** — 在下拉框中选择或输入标签，可用于对产品分类管理；多个标签以逗号分隔。"
msgstr ""
"**Tags** — pick or type tags from the drop-down to categorize the product; "
"comma-separated for multiple tags."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:29
msgid ""
"**板长 / 板宽** — 直接输入已知的 PCB 尺寸，单位毫米，通常来自产品图纸或 SMT 工单。尺寸在产品创建后固定，向导不再通过相机测量尺寸。"
msgstr ""
"**Board Length / Board Width** — type in the known PCB dimensions in "
"millimeters, usually taken from the product drawing or the SMT work order. "
"The dimensions are fixed once the product is created; the wizard no longer "
"measures them with the camera."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:32
msgid "检测类型、自动编程参数与健康检查不再在本步骤设置，已移至第三步 **配置自动编程**，在拼接出的完整图像前完成配置。"
msgstr ""
"Inspection types, auto-programming parameters, and health checks are no "
"longer set on this step — they have moved to Step 3, **Configure Auto-"
"Program**, where they are configured in front of the stitched full image."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:-1
msgid "自动编程向导第一步 基本信息：产品名称、标签、PCB 尺寸（板长度 / 板宽度）输入"
msgstr ""
"Auto-Programming Wizard Step 1, Basic Info: product name, labels, and PCB "
"dimensions (board length / width) input"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:38
msgid "**第二步：上板与拍摄**"
msgstr "**Step 2: Conveyor & Capture**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:40
msgid "本步骤将\"上板\"与\"完整拍摄\"合并为一个连续动作："
msgstr ""
"This step merges loading the board and full capture into one continuous "
"action:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:42
msgid "将 PCB 平整放置于传送带中央，选择传送带并点击 **锁定**。"
msgstr ""
"Place the PCB flat in the center of the conveyor, select the conveyor, and "
"click **Lock**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:43
msgid "在线版本中确认或调整 **传送带宽度**。"
msgstr "On the online version, confirm or adjust the **Conveyor Width**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:44
msgid "点击 **进板**，等待 PCB 自动输送至拍摄区域。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Load Board** and wait for the PCB to be conveyed to the capture "
"area."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:45
msgid "点击 **拍摄2D图像**，系统联动相机与传送带分区采集并拼接生成完整 PCB 图像，拼接结果直接显示在本步骤的画布中。"
msgstr ""
"Click **Capture 2D Image**; the system coordinates the camera and conveyor "
"to acquire the board in tiles and stitch the full PCB image, which is shown "
"directly on this step's canvas."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:47
msgid ""
"请务必使用洁净、无缺陷的良品板（Golden board）。必要时可在该界面调整 **曝光时间**、**增益**、**gamma** "
"等相机参数后重新拍摄。拼接图像满意后点击 **下一步**。"
msgstr ""
"Always use a clean, defect-free **Golden board**. If needed, tune camera "
"parameters such as **Exposure**, **Gain**, and **gamma** on this screen and "
"re-capture. Once the stitched image looks right, click **Next**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:-1
msgid "上板与拍摄步骤：右侧传送带控制（锁定 / 进板 / 拍摄2D）与相机参数，左侧拼接出的完整 PCB 图像"
msgstr ""
"Conveyor & Capture step: conveyor controls (Lock / PCB In / Capture 2D) and "
"camera parameters on the right, the stitched full PCB image on the left"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:53
msgid "相机参数会随产品一同创建，并在检测时沿用同一组参数采集，确保编程图像与检测图像一致。如效果不佳，可重新拍摄覆盖上一版本。"
msgstr ""
"Camera parameters are saved with the product and reused at inspection time, "
"so the programming image and the inspection image stay consistent. If the "
"result isn't acceptable, re-capture to overwrite the prior version."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:55
msgid "**相机参数**"
msgstr "**Camera parameters**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:-1
msgid "相机参数示意"
msgstr "Camera parameters"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:61
msgid "绝大多数情况下，只需调整 **曝光时间** 让图像亮度合适即可；**增益** 与 **gamma** 用于色彩或暗部细节微调，非必要不修改。"
msgstr ""
"In most cases just tune **Exposure** to set image brightness. **Gain** and "
"**gamma** are reserved for fine-tuning color or shadow detail — leave them "
"alone unless you have to."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:63
msgid "**第三步：配置自动编程**"
msgstr "**Step 3: Configure Auto-Program**"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:65
msgid ""
"在 **配置自动编程** 步骤中，系统显示上一步拼接出的完整图像（只读）。在此定义检测区域、拼板信息、检测类型与参数、健康检查，完成后点击 "
"**下一步**。"
msgstr ""
"On the **Configure Auto-Program** step, the system shows the full image "
"stitched in the previous step (read-only). Here you define the inspection "
"region, panelization, inspection types and parameters, and health checks; "
"then click **Next**."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:67
msgid "**定义检测区域** — 点击 **定义区域**，支持两种方式："
msgstr ""
"**Define the inspection region** — click **Define Region**; two ways are "
"supported:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:69
msgid "**设置矩形检测区域** — 在图像上拖动框选矩形范围。"
msgstr ""
"**Set Rect Inspection Region** — drag to box a rectangular area on the "
"image."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:70
msgid "**设置多边形检测区域** — 在图像上 **按顺时针方向** 依次点击多个顶点，**最后双击鼠标** 完成多边形区域。"
msgstr ""
"**Set Polygon Inspection Region** — click vertices in **clockwise** order on"
" the image, then **double-click** to finish the polygon."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:72
msgid ""
"检测区域决定自动编程 AI 识别和生成检测框的范围，通常框选整板；若需排除治具边缘，可适当收缩。必须在进入下一步前完成定义，否则系统会提示错误。"
msgstr ""
"The inspection region defines the area within which auto-programming detects"
" and generates inspection boxes — usually the whole board; shrink it if "
"fixture edges should be excluded. It must be defined before you advance, "
"otherwise the system reports an error."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:74
msgid ""
"**拼板** — 若产品为拼板，开启 **启用拼板** 开关并填写 **行数** / **列数**。启用拼板时，上方检测区域必须绘制在 "
"**单个代表性子板** 周围，而非整块拼板；自动编程结束后系统会据此自动构建拼板阵列，详见 :doc:`auto_programming` "
"中的\"编程后的自动处理\"一节。"
msgstr ""
"**Panelization** — if the product is panelized, turn on the **Enable "
"panelization** switch and enter **Num of Rows** / **Num of Cols**. When "
"panelization is on, the inspection region above must be drawn around **a "
"single representative sub-board**, not the whole panel; after auto-"
"programming the system builds the panel array accordingly. See the \"Post-"
"programming automation\" section in :doc:`auto_programming`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:76
msgid "**自动编程检测类型：** — 勾选需要 AI 自动生成 ROI 的检测类型。每种类型下可展开选择具体的封装子类："
msgstr ""
"**AI-modelled inspection types:** — check the inspection types you want the "
"AI to auto-generate ROIs for. Each type can be expanded to pick specific "
"package sub-classes:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:78
msgid "**本体** — 检测元件是否贴装在位（本体检测）。"
msgstr ""
"**Body** — detects whether the component is mounted in place (body "
"inspection)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:79
msgid "**极性** — 检测极性方向是否正确。"
msgstr "**Polarity** — verifies the polarity orientation."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:80
msgid "**焊点** — 检测焊点质量（润湿、偏移等）。"
msgstr ""
"**Solder Joint** — assesses solder-joint quality (wetting, offset, and so "
"on)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:81
msgid "**IC引脚** — 检测 IC 引脚状态（翘脚、桥连、缺失等），适用于 SOIC / SOP / QFP 等细间距器件。"
msgstr ""
"**IC Lead** — inspects IC lead condition (lifted leads, bridges, missing "
"leads, and so on); used for fine-pitch packages such as SOIC / SOP / QFP."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:82
msgid "**文字** — 检测元件丝印文字（OCR）。"
msgstr "**Text** — reads the component silkscreen text (OCR)."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:83
msgid "**焊盘沾胶** — 检测焊盘上的红胶污染。"
msgstr "**Glue on Pad** — detects red-glue contamination on solder pads."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:84
msgid "**元件本体颜色** — 检测元件本体颜色，适用于 CRM、LED 等有颜色要求的元件。"
msgstr ""
"**Body Color** — checks the component body color; used for parts with color "
"requirements such as CRM and LED."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:85
msgid "**DIP** — 检测波峰焊后的 DIP 焊点，包含炉后（dip_solder）和炉前（dip_pin）两种封装子类。"
msgstr ""
"**DIP** — inspects DIP solder joints after wave soldering; covers both post-"
"wave (``dip_solder``) and pre-wave (``dip_pin``) sub-classes."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:88
msgid "不同类型的封装可展开勾选，例如\"本体\"类型下包含 Capacitor、Resistor、LED、QFP 等。DIP 类型默认不选中，需手动启用。"
msgstr ""
"Each type expands to package-level checkboxes — for example, **Body** covers"
" Capacitor, Resistor, LED, QFP, and others. **DIP** is off by default and "
"must be enabled explicitly."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:90
msgid "**自动编程参数** — 根据已勾选的检测类型，展开对应的参数配置，仅当对应类型启用时显示："
msgstr ""
"**Auto Programming Parameters** — expand the parameter block for the "
"inspection types you checked; each block is shown only when its type is "
"enabled:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:92
msgid "**DIP 参数** — DIP 检测启用时显示："
msgstr "**DIP parameters** — shown when DIP inspection is enabled:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:94
msgid "**邻近距离 (像素)** — DIP 焊点间邻近距离阈值（像素），用于判断相邻焊点归属。"
msgstr ""
"**Adjacency distance (pixels)** — adjacency threshold between DIP joints (in"
" pixels), used to decide which joints group together."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:95
msgid "**ROI 扩展 (%)** — DIP ROI 的边缘向外扩展比例。"
msgstr "**ROI expansion (%)** — outward edge expansion ratio for the DIP ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:97
msgid "**桥接** — 勾选复选框以启用桥接检测；取消勾选则禁用。"
msgstr ""
"**Bridge** — check the box to enable bridge inspection; uncheck to disable."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:99
msgid "**邻近距离 (像素)** — 桥接检测的邻近距离阈值（像素）；禁用时不可编辑。"
msgstr ""
"**Adjacency distance (pixels)** — adjacency threshold for bridge detection "
"(in pixels); not editable when disabled."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:101
msgid "**焊盘沾胶参数** — 焊盘沾胶检测启用时显示："
msgstr ""
"**Glue on Pad parameters** — shown when Glue on Pad inspection is enabled:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:103
msgid "**ROI 扩展 (%)** — 焊盘沾胶 ROI 的边缘扩展比例，支持负值（缩小 ROI）。"
msgstr ""
"**ROI expansion (%)** — edge expansion ratio for the Glue-on-Pad ROI; "
"negative values shrink the ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:105
msgid "**元件本体颜色参数** — 元件本体颜色检测启用时显示："
msgstr ""
"**Component Body Color parameters** — shown when Component Body Color "
"inspection is enabled:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:107
msgid "**本体 ROI 面积 (%)** — 元件本体颜色 ROI 占本体区域的面积比例。"
msgstr ""
"**Body ROI area (%)** — proportion of the body region used by the Body Color"
" ROI."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:109
msgid "**健康检查** — 设置自动编程完成后的质量验证选项："
msgstr ""
"**Health checks** — quality-verification options that run after Auto-"
"Programming finishes:"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:111
msgid "**数量检查** — 校验每个元件是否具有期望数量的焊点及 IC 引脚；有 CAD 封装信息时按封装精确匹配引脚数。"
msgstr ""
"**Count check** — verifies that every component carries the expected number "
"of solder joints and IC leads. When CAD package data is available, lead "
"counts are matched per package."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:112
msgid "**质量检查** — 校验焊点对称性、IC 引脚一致性及排阻引脚覆盖率。"
msgstr ""
"**Quality check** — verifies solder-joint symmetry, IC lead consistency, and"
" resistor-array lead coverage."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:-1
msgid "配置自动编程步骤：左侧检测区域绘制工具与拼接图像，右侧拼板 / 检测类型 / 检测参数 / 健康检查折叠面板"
msgstr ""
"Configure Auto-Program step: region-drawing tools and the stitched image on "
"the left, the Panelization / Inspection Types / Auto Programming Parameters "
"/ Health Checks collapse panels on the right"

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:118
msgid ""
"完成 **配置自动编程** 步骤后点击 **下一步**，进入 **添加CAD (可选)** 步骤；可选择全自动编程、半自动编程或手动编程，详见 "
":doc:`auto_programming`。"
msgstr ""
"After finishing the **Configure Auto-Program** step, click **Next** to reach"
" the **Add CAD (Optional)** step; from there you can choose full auto-"
"programming, semi-auto programming, or manual programming. See "
":doc:`auto_programming`."

#: ../../source/complete_user_guide/features/create_product.rst:120
msgid "**自动检测支持类型总览**"
msgstr "**Auto-detection support overview**"

